{"tid":325313,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Pokémon go奇遇","createTime":"2017-07-17T06:29:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T14:02:05.000Z","uid":49073,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e4ad9febe5968a3559f575b3ddbb65eb2ea825b6","tid":325313,"uid":49073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:29:12.000Z","msg":"好少可專登開post<br />\n岩岩放lunch時間見到有耿鬼 battle打<br />\n食完飯行去打下 點知去到入唔到個範圍之餘<br />\n又開始落大雨<br />\n我又唔記得帶把傘出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n咁岩遇到位師兄 束頭髮黑衫帶眼鏡 行黎打<br />\n又傘埋我搵個岩位打 試左陣都唔得<br />\n第一場佢同街人打 打唔過<br />\n我又咁岩入得返<br />\n到佢唔係擂台圈入面 所以要走開搵位<br />\n<br />\n打完哂捉埋 依舊好大雨 諗住有排等雨停<br />\n估到師兄行返黎話傘埋我<br />\n明明唔同路都送我一程 仲交流左陣心得<br />\n臨尾到埗握左個手 知左佢知名叫E字頭<br />\n<br />\n其實我唔知位師兄會唔會上呢度<br />\n但斷估唔會上香討所以黎搏一搏<br />\n<br />\n非常感謝你出手送一程 唔係小弟實變落湯雞"},{"pid":"bdd60deb6244a0dd8251d533643ea188a9484b03","tid":325313,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:05:50.000Z","msg":"THIS"},{"pid":"a2e7625442f37ac2fdbd668ca705461d33d42563","tid":325313,"uid":3232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:15:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>THIS</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Is</span></span>"},{"pid":"e81301d5fd2ee631886e08ab23a1f14a6c6ffe9d","tid":325313,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:16:15.000Z","msg":"IS"},{"pid":"3cbb4167e8cedca8eb04a8865f127444e23203b4","tid":325313,"uid":4448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:17:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Great</span><span style=\"color: red;\"></span>"},{"pid":"2ef1280453d2cb7ebadfcd6cbba2f86e2985a375","tid":325313,"uid":54995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:22:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef74d38eed15c6d57f75401f21fbbf630ec1fe7d","tid":3253